## âœ… I. **Submatrix / Subarray Sum Problems**

Focus: sum of rectangular regions, optimization, prefix sum, or Kadaneâ€™s.

| Problem Type                          | Techniques Used                            | Example Problems      |
| ------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------ | --------------------- |
| Sum of submatrix (single query)       | 2D Prefix Sum                              | \[i,j] to \[x,y]      |
| Sum of submatrix (multiple queries)   | Precompute 2D prefix                       |                       |
| Maximum sum submatrix (any size)      | Kadaneâ€™s 2D                                |                       |
| Maximum sum submatrix under a value K | Kadaneâ€™s + BST (TreeSet) or Sliding Window | Hard variant          |
| Count submatrices with sum K          | Prefix sum + HashMap                       | Like subarray sum = k |

