## âœ… II. **Matrix Traversal Patterns**

Focus: simulate directions, recursion, boundaries

| Pattern                              | Techniques Used              | Example Problems              |
| ------------------------------------ | ---------------------------- | ----------------------------- |
| Spiral order traversal               | Simulation, direction arrays | Spiral Matrix I & II          |
| Diagonal traversal                   | Coordinate manipulation      | Diagonal Zig-Zag of 2D matrix |
| Boundary traversal                   | Layer-by-layer simulation    |                               |
| Snake pattern traversal              | Even/odd row trick           |                               |
| Zigzag traversal (used in trees too) | Queue + direction toggle     |                               |

---

## âœ… III. **Matrix Transformations / Modifications**

Focus: in-place changes, coordinate formulas

| Problem Type                        | Techniques Used                         | Example Problems              |
| ----------------------------------- | --------------------------------------- | ----------------------------- |
| Rotate matrix by 90/180/270 degrees | Transpose + reverse                     | Rotate Image (LC 48)          |
| Transpose of matrix                 | Swap `matrix[i][j]` with `matrix[j][i]` |                               |
| Set Matrix Zeroes                   | In-place marking                        | LC 73                         |
| Flip image horizontally/vertically  | Row or column reversal                  | Flip and Invert Binary Matrix |
| Shift matrix                        | Coordinate mapping                      | Shift 2D Grid (LC 1260)       |

---

## âœ… IV. **Matrix Path Problems**

Focus: DFS, BFS, DP

| Problem Type                                  | Techniques Used     | Example Problems       |
| --------------------------------------------- | ------------------- | ---------------------- |
| Number of paths from top-left to bottom-right | DP, memoization     | Unique Paths I/II      |
| Word Search / Letter Matching                 | DFS + backtracking  | Word Search (LC 79)    |
| Island counting / flood fill                  | DFS/BFS             | Number of Islands      |
| Longest increasing path in matrix             | DFS + memoization   | Hard problem           |
| Matrix traversal with constraints             | BFS + visited\[]\[] | Shortest Path problems |

